11 "Panther's Quest" Sebastian Montes Paul Giacoppo  November 17, 2010 (2010-11-17) 011 

T'Challa, the new Black Panther, meets the Avengers and tells them that his country has been overthrown by Man-Ape.
 As the Avengers arrive in Wakanda, not only do they have to help T'Challa reclaim his family's throne and country,
